> $ more example.rb
> require 'rubygems'
> require 'ffi'

> extend FFI::Library
> ffi_lib './libsample.so'
> attach_function :foo, :foo, [:int], :int


You need to enclose the above in a module.
e.g.
module LibSample
  extend FFI::Library
  fi_lib './libsample.so'
  attach_function :foo, :foo, [:int], :int
end

And call it as
LibSample.foo(1)
